      "content": "i just don't have the time or money to go to urgent care right now honestly. it's probably just a bad strain since it happened when i tripped. if i just take some ibuprofen and do the ice/elevation thing for like 3 or 4 days do you think it'll be okay? like, is there any reason i *really* need an Xray if it stops throbbing in a couple days?",
